channel.title: Looking for GWD Team
channel.description:
So.... my friend and I want to do BGWD for the first time. We will be using this guide: http://www.tip.it/runescape/?page=bandos_stronghold.htm#ls
If you have the required stats and could be on at 11pm PST (gmt -8) today, please leave a reply. Thanks.
We want 5 people:
[ol][li]Davidi2[/li] [li]Psychochck7 (my friend)[/li] [li]Primadude[/li] [li]NEEDED[/li] [li]NEEDED (tank)[/li][/ol]
